<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls2-splithandle.xml">SplitHandle</db:link> provides attached properties for <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls2-splitview.xml">SplitView</db:link> handles.</db:para>
